    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato </strong>and <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> to a separate bowl with the <strong>quick-pickled onion </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion salad</strong></p>",
